originalText.text: Let me start off by saying. Don’t think you’re going to get something for free. That’s not a bad thing. They give you a Focus professional photographer. I forgot her name but she was awesome. I felt very comfortable. I’m 59 years old I’ve never done anything like this before in my life. Hair and make up purely professional and awesome. Everybody made me feel totally at ease. I was encouraged to get something more expensive than I could afford. However, I explain to them I just could not afford it. All in all they were very cool with that. I did walk away with some very awesome pictures. The ones I had posted on Facebook people are crazy about. So now with these great pictures that I walked away with. I have some work to do they explain that to me. Totally a fair deal. Enjoyable. Straight shooters.

originalText.text: This was my first time visiting this place.It was in a tall building on the eighth floor.Me and my daughter was greeted at the door by a respectfully soft tone women.She took us to a nice spacey clean furnished room.There were couches,magazines, and a flat tv to watch. There also were paintings, and sculptures in the room with a clear glass door.There was also mixed soothing music playing.The staff treated my daughter with dignity and respect!!They also did my daughters makeup and made her look wonderful!!!Then they took wonderful ,flawless pictures of my daughter.They are also helping my daughter fulfill her dream of becoming a model!! I recommend this place to all my friends and family!!

originalText.text: Located in the heart of midtown Manhattan this studio offers nothing but brilliance. The staff is incredibly polite, you will notice it from the moment you call their office. I had pre photoshoot consultation with Laura and got clear instructions about what to expect on the day of the photoshoot. Bari did my make up and Jay was my photographer, both did a brilliant job. The studio is easy to locate with parking garage located just across the street. I loved every bit of my experience and would highly recommend their services. I had tears of joy when I saw my photos. The staff continued to work with me till the end and made sure I leave as a happy client.
